act.article:
2 Definitions.—In these rules, unless the context otherwise requires,—
a “Act” means the Wild Life (Protection) Act, 1972 (53 of 1972);
b “expert or professional member” means a member of the Tiger Conservation Authority, appointed under clause (d) of sub-section (2) of section 38L of the Act;
c “Tiger Conservation Authority” means the National Tiger Conservation Authority constituted under section 38L of the Act.
